zm_isolation_x Originally made by hecatomb for Headcrab Hunter as hh_isolation, with his permission I took it and re-made it to be ZM compatible. 85% of the map was done by hecatomb, so all credit goes to him. I added some new rooms, changed the spawns, edited the Nerve Gas along with the alarm and stuff, and made a radar map. I also added a new way out of spawn -- there's a connection to the vent system to the right of the door. I did that to help the crowding issue. Statistics: 48 Spawns Cubemaps Radar Map Nerve Gas This is a hybrid escape/camping map. Players have the option of setting off the Nerve Gas which will kill players in the lower levels of the map. The outside, portions of the vents, and the nerve gas room itself along with the upper levels are safe from the gas, but a lot of good camping spots are in areas that would be flooded by the gas, so when the sirens go off you gotta fight your way out or be killed. The door where the Nerve Gas button is starts off locked. You can see in screenshot #2 the un-locker panel. Press e on it to unlock the door. When you press the gas button, sirens will go off in affected areas, and the red emergency lights will activate. Gas is released after 60 seconds, for a 10 second period. It takes 10 more seconds to dissipate, whereupon the alarms and lights will turn off and the lower levels can be accessed again. I have a long gameplay video that shows the gas sequence among other things: If you have any questions or comments please let me know!! - Natalya

After doing allot of work on thismap,its finaly done.
it started as the idea to make 36rooms connected to eachother by breakable doors,so that you would notknow where you would end up.
you could encounter some brain hungry zombies or some camping ct's.
or maybe the exit to a higher level.
if you escaped out of the cellar you will reach a small dome with a fortres inside it,inside there you get a great camping spot. 
also some higher grounds that can only be reached by jumping on some boxes.
once you go higher up the map youwill go outdoors,its almost pitchblack except for some streetlanterns.there, you will find some stacked containers wich will have to be jumped if you want to go up top.
once you go down the hill you will reach the street with lots of destroyed cars and trucks,perfect for chases.

i used allot of occluders so you will get good fps
i hd allot of fun making and testing this map,i hope you will enjoy playing it.

Strange map, inspired by another ZM map (name, I cannot remember). The beginning is just a sort of a dash to get to safety (player spawn in a building with no buyzones, 12 weapons placed at a distance, and a closing ceiling). They get to the end, and there is just a drop into a pit of.. strangers. Which is really just a transporter-hole. From there, the map becomes a bit less hurried, but far less "usual". 

This is an odd map that will keep most players pretty much weaponless until halfway through, but it's all thought out (and there are buyzones, so don't fret). The last staging area of the map is a shrunk, modified version of my other map, zm_tarantism.

Enjoy, and if you add this or any other map to your server, please let me know (so I can play :) ).
